{"tid":1920163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【事實係法律保障唔到你】","createTime":"2020-03-11T09:29:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T01:47:01.000Z","uid":320135,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f384a2aa0cbf0b614e46d63a7065dc5a80b6d2fc","tid":1920163,"uid":320135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:29:26.000Z","msg":"【事實係法律保障唔到你】<br />\n<br />\n「我冇嘢講」、｢我要見律師｣、｢我要驗傷｣相信而家已經係大家嘅常識，但係呢三句金句基本上都係建基於法治未死，依然有險可守底下。<br />\n<br />\n當你話｢我要見律師｣，狗可以唔比你見。<br />\n當你話｢我冇嘢講｣，狗就由唔講咬到你講。<br />\n當你話｢我要驗傷｣，狗就話佢未咬夠。<br />\n<br />\n如果你仲未明白香港有幾黑暗，睇下今日發生左咩事。<br />\n同一單案入面，喺大家都識講｢我冇嘢講｣呢個常識下，六個被告有兩個｢警戒｣下承認有部份參與、一個｢警戒｣下供出左某啲事情。如果｢我冇嘢講｣真係保障到被告行使緘默權，為何要開口？<br />\n係佢哋戇鳩？定係拳頭鐵棍、威嚇搞家人女友、定係比人塞左個頭入洗手盤行水刑？<br />\n<br />\n另外三個，其中一個係用黎威脅嘅人質，剩底兩個就庭都已經上唔到，瞓左喺醫院入面。原因唔洗講，你都知點解，有一個以後都未必行得返。<br />\n<br />\n當然仲有命上庭嘅被告有向法庭投訴，但法官就合埋雙眼咩都睇唔到、發生咩事都冇可疑，一如以往咁以正常程序審理各被告嘅保釋條件，一如以往咁拒絕各被告保釋，一如以往咁將佢哋還押。<br />\n<br />\n面對住一條冇呼吸、冇心跳、開始發臭嘅腐屍，你唔需要醫生張死亡證去證明阿法治先生佢已經死左。<br />\n<br />\n無錯你未必有份建立呢個荒謬嘅世界，但係每一個人都有責任去阻止呢種荒謬延續落去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1546925482228025/posts/2590424777878085/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1546925482228025%2Fposts%2F2590424777878085%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=b2810e2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1546925482228025/posts/2590424777878085/?d=n</a><br />\nFrom 本土民主前線 <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/forltkelectionsoffice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fforltkelectionsoffice&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=6def7aad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/forltkelectionsoffice</a>"},{"pid":"e534073dad8bf18aa5d77965676ef80ae6f3575c","tid":1920163,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:29:53.000Z","msg":"死亡證 哈"},{"pid":"cb13b2dd6ad9f9dd567eceeb10a855db68442d83","tid":1920163,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:30:20.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"e8fed9514ae27d564e64473481237a121fa0908c","tid":1920163,"uid":177168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:30:21.000Z","msg":"絕對支持武裝革命，但好需要海外手足幫手"},{"pid":"8944dbc69feede15803ee67660ec970e58cddfc1","tid":1920163,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:33:01.000Z","msg":"仲敢講係制度問題真係笑死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜咁耐以黎有人在乎過制度咩"},{"pid":"932271fe76775a64045a9c956800ff57e537c247","tid":1920163,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e534073dad8bf18aa5d77965676ef80ae6f3575c","tid":1920163,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:29:53.000Z","msg":"死亡證 哈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:33:29.000Z","msg":"OMDB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e1207d40546eea5653a658c1e58675a08f8ddb","tid":1920163,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8fed9514ae27d564e64473481237a121fa0908c","tid":1920163,"uid":177168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:30:21.000Z","msg":"絕對支持武裝革命，但好需要海外手足幫手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:33:58.000Z","msg":"小心啲啦..."},{"pid":"1d6ec7a99b9ddcd505c6bb3ba10587b2f01b1ebc","tid":1920163,"uid":261773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:34:57.000Z","msg":"sad but true <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9080242949fb1968068bd7dc6bc1402159fe71","tid":1920163,"uid":14069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:36:47.000Z","msg":"【復仇】入嚟放低證據<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1920114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1920114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n法律保障唔到 英國可能得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c3995a746bfef23a88d55387fa3570f6236a5c"